doctype html
html(lang='en')
  head
    meta(charset='utf-8')
    meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no')
    meta(name='description', content='Learn about Purple Vector Operations, a Tasmania-based provider of non-clinical medical practice support services.')
    meta(name='author', content='Purple Vector Operations')
    title About | Purple Vector Operations
    link(rel='icon', type='image/x-icon', href='assets/favicon.ico')
    script(src='https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v6.3.0/js/all.js', crossorigin='anonymous')
    link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Montserrat:400,700', rel='stylesheet', type='text/css')
    link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto+Slab:400,100,300,700', rel='stylesheet', type='text/css')
    link(href='css/styles.css', rel='stylesheet')
  body#page-top
    nav#mainNav.navbar.navbar-expand-lg.navbar-dark.fixed-top
      .container
        a.navbar-brand(href='index.html') Purple Vector Operations
        button.navbar-toggler(type='button', data-bs-toggle='collapse', data-bs-target='#navbarResponsive', aria-controls='navbarResponsive', aria-expanded='false', aria-label='Toggle navigation')
          | Menu
          i.fas.fa-bars.ms-1
        #navbarResponsive.collapse.navbar-collapse
          ul.navbar-nav.text-uppercase.ms-auto.py-4.py-lg-0
            li.nav-item
              a.nav-link(href='index.html') Home
            li.nav-item
              a.nav-link.active(href='about.html') About
            li.nav-item
              a.nav-link(href='services.html') Services
            li.nav-item
              a.nav-link(href='index.html#contact') Contact

    header.masthead(style='padding-top: 12rem; padding-bottom: 6rem;')
      .container
        .masthead-subheading About Purple Vector Operations
        .masthead-heading.text-uppercase Non-clinical support for modern medical practices
        p.text-white-50.mx-auto(style='max-width: 760px;')
          | Purple Vector Operations helps practices and clinicians reduce admin friction, clean up systems, manage records, and improve day-to-day workflow without replacing their existing staff or IT providers.

    section.page-section
      .container
        .row.gx-5.align-items-center
          .col-lg-6
            h2.section-heading.text-uppercase What PVO does
            p.text-muted
              | Purple Vector Operations provides practical, healthcare-focused operational support for clinics and individual clinicians across Tasmania. Services are strictly non-clinical and focus on administration, systems, workflow optimisation, records handling, digitisation, and compliance-aware processes.
            p.text-muted
              | The aim is simple: remove unnecessary admin load, make practice systems easier to use, and help clinics move from messy, manual, outdated processes into cleaner and more sustainable workflows.
          .col-lg-6
            .p-4.bg-light.rounded-4.shadow-sm
              h4.text-uppercase.mb-3 At a glance
              ul.text-muted.mb-0
                li Tasmania-based support for clinics and clinicians
                li Non-clinical administrative, systems, and workflow services
                li Works alongside existing practice staff and IT providers
                li Strong focus on secure handling and healthcare-aware processes

    section.page-section.bg-light
      .container
        .text-center
          h2.section-heading.text-uppercase Why it exists
          h3.section-subheading.text-muted Built for the work that clinics never seem to have time to finish.
        .row.text-center.mt-5
          .col-md-4
            span.fa-stack.fa-4x
              i.fas.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x.text-primary
              i.fas.fa-folder-open.fa-stack-1x.fa-inverse
            h4.my-3 Legacy records and admin backlog
            p.text-muted
              | Paper files, messy folders, old workflows, and half-finished system setups quietly waste time every week.
          .col-md-4
            span.fa-stack.fa-4x
              i.fas.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x.text-primary
              i.fas.fa-gears.fa-stack-1x.fa-inverse
            h4.my-3 Better systems without full upheaval
            p.text-muted
              | PVO improves the operational layer around a clinic so staff can work faster without a giant, painful system overhaul.
          .col-md-4
            span.fa-stack.fa-4x
              i.fas.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x.text-primary
              i.fas.fa-shield-halved.fa-stack-1x.fa-inverse
            h4.my-3 Secure, practical handling
            p.text-muted
              | Workflows are designed with privacy, access control, and sensible data handling in mind. Because chaos plus patient data is a terrible hobby.

    section#about.page-section
      .container
        .text-center
          h2.section-heading.text-uppercase How PVO works
          h3.section-subheading.text-muted Support that fits around real practices, not fantasy ones.
        ul.timeline
          li
            .timeline-image
              h4
                | Step 1
            .timeline-panel
              .timeline-heading
                h4 Initial review
                h4.subheading Understand the practice properly
              .timeline-body
                p.text-muted
                  | Review the clinic's current setup, software, records processes, bottlenecks, and support needs before recommending anything.
          li.timeline-inverted
            .timeline-image
              h4
                | Step 2
            .timeline-panel
              .timeline-heading
                h4 Scope the work
                h4.subheading Retainer, project, or one-off support
              .timeline-body
                p.text-muted
                  | Services can be structured as ongoing support, defined project work, scanning programs, or targeted consulting depending on what the clinic actually needs.
          li
            .timeline-image
              h4
                | Step 3
            .timeline-panel
              .timeline-heading
                h4 Implement and tidy
                h4.subheading Clean up the operational mess
              .timeline-body
                p.text-muted
                  | Improve workflows, prepare templates, digitise records, coordinate software support, and reduce manual admin burden in ways staff can realistically maintain.
          li.timeline-inverted
            .timeline-image
              h4
                | Step 4
            .timeline-panel
              .timeline-heading
                h4 Ongoing support
                h4.subheading Keep things working
              .timeline-body
                p.text-muted
                  | Maintain systems, perform routine checks, refine workflows, and provide practical support as the practice evolves.
          li.timeline-inverted
            .timeline-image
              h4
                | Built
                br
                | For
                br
                | Clinics

    section.page-section.bg-light
      .container
        .row.justify-content-center
          .col-lg-10
            .text-center.mb-5
              h2.section-heading.text-uppercase Scope and boundaries
              h3.section-subheading.text-muted Clear, boring, important boundaries. The legal department of reality insists.
            .row.g-4
              .col-md-6
                .card.h-100.border-0.shadow-sm
                  .card-body
                    h4.card-title.text-uppercase Included focus
                    ul.text-muted.mb-0
                      li Administrative and operational support
                      li Workflow optimisation and systems cleanup
                      li Xestro and practice software assistance
                      li Paper-to-digital conversion and records organisation
                      li Secure handling, templates, documentation, and process support
              .col-md-6
                .card.h-100.border-0.shadow-sm
                  .card-body
                    h4.card-title.text-uppercase Not provided
                    ul.text-muted.mb-0
                      li Clinical advice, diagnosis, or treatment
                      li Medico-legal opinions
                      li Independent replacement of the clinic's IT provider
                      li Clinical decision-making of any kind

    section.page-section
      .container
        .row.justify-content-center.text-center
          .col-lg-8
            h2.section-heading.text-uppercase Ready to talk?
            p.text-muted.mb-4
              | Whether you need help with Xestro, workflow clean-up, admin support, or a paper-to-digital backlog, PVO can be engaged for practical support that fits around your existing setup.
            a.btn.btn-primary.btn-xl.text-uppercase.me-3(href='services.html') View Services
            a.btn.btn-dark.btn-xl.text-uppercase(href='index.html#contact') Contact PVO

    footer.footer.py-4
      .container
        .row.align-items-center
          .col-lg-4.text-lg-start Copyright © Purple Vector Operations 2026
          .col-lg-4.my-3.my-lg-0
            a.btn.btn-dark.btn-social.mx-2(href='mailto:admin@purplevectoroperations.com', aria-label='Email Purple Vector Operations')
              i.fas.fa-envelope
          .col-lg-4.text-lg-end
            a.link-dark.text-decoration-none.me-3(href='about.html') About
            a.link-dark.text-decoration-none(href='services.html') Services

    script(src='https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js')
    script(src='js/scripts.js')
